Show HN: Record how your day went and view GitHub-like graphs and stats
text:
Hello HN!

a day in my life is a daily mood tracker app that helps you record the quality of your life. With this app, you can easily track your mood on a daily basis and generate weekly, monthly, and yearly GitHub-like graphs and stats to gain insight into your emotional well-being.

Features a simple and intuitive interface that allows you to quickly and easily record your daily mood. You can view stats and graphs that show how your mood changes over time, allowing you to identify trends and gain insight into your overall well-being.

Take print-outs of your graphs or simply share with friends, family, or the world.

Made with React Native.

Let me know what you guys think! :)
